html
	head
		link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css')
		link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.97.5/css/materialize.min.css")
		link(rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/index.css")
	body
		include ./includes/header.jade
		h2(class="center text-orange") Student Contact Form
		h5(class="center text-orange") When a prospective student writes in to the admissions office looking for direct contact, the admissions office will forward their e-mail on to a student with similar interests, home country, or industry. After reading their e-mail, please notify admissions if you will respond to the student. IF you choose not to respond, for any reason, please let us know so we can find another contact. The candidate will not know you have refused to be a contact for them.
		div(class="row container text-purple")
			div(class="row")
				form(class="col s4")
					p Name
					div(class="input-field col s12")
						input(placeholder="First Name" type="text")
					div(class="input-field col s12")
						input(placeholder="Last Name" type="text")
			div(class="row")
				form(class="col s4")
					p Email
					div(class="input-field col s12")
						input(placeholder="Email" type="email")
			div(class="row")
				div(class="col s4")
					p Program
						div(class="col s12")
							select
								option(value="" disabled selected) Select a Program
								option(value='2 Year MBA') 2 Year MBA
								option(value='1 Year MBA') 1 Year MBA			
								option(value='MMM') MMM
								option(value='JD-MBA') JD-MBA
			
	include ./includes/footer.jade
	script(src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.0.min.js")
	script(src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.97.5/js/materialize.min.js")
	script(src="/public/js/survey.js")